cc:Work.dc:description: A glance at F-Spot's key for managing photos.

text.tspan: Relive Memories with F-Spot Photo Manager

flowRoot.flowPara: Ubuntu comes with F-Spot Photo Manager a terrific utility to manage all of your photos. Plug your phone or camera into the computer and discover a really easy way to manage, display, organise, edit and share your photos with your friends.
Adjust colour, remove red-eye or make them artistic, F-Spot comes with a built-in easy to use tool to touch up your photos to make that memory crystal clear.
Never get lost in your photo collection again, F-Spot comes with a timeline to view images by date and features a useful tagging functionality to group similiar photos together.
